TI  - How does internet use promote joint adoption of sustainable agricultural practices? Evidence from rice farmers in China
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Sustainable agricultural practices
KW  - joint adoption of technology
KW  - internet use
KW  - farmers
