TI  - Boosting the adoption of sustainable land-use systems for achieving Colombian land-based climate action and peacebuilding goals
T2  - WORLD DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Farm-level adoption factors
KW  - Cocoa
KW  - Agroforestry
KW  - Environmental peacebuilding
KW  - Colombia
