KW  - SMALLHOLDER FARMERS
KW  - MANAGEMENT PRACTICE
KW  - TIPPING POINTS
KW  - AGROFORESTRY
KW  - INNOVATIONS
KW  - DETERMINANTS
KW  - POLICIES
KW  - DRIVERS
