TI  - The Role of Crop-Livestock Integration on Economic Resilience Among Small-Holder Farmers: A Case Study of Asayita District, Afar Region, Ethiopia
T2  - ADVANCES IN AGRICULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - Asayita district
