TI  - Drivers of use and adoption of bundled climate-smart agriculture and climate information services in Northern Ghana
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Climate-smart agriculture
