TI  - How does inter-annual variability of attainable yield affect the magnitude of yield gaps for wheat and maize? An analysis at ten sites
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Inter-annual yield variability
KW  - Yield gap analysis
KW  - Wheat
KW  - Maize
