TI  - The small pelagic fishery of the Pemba Channel, Tanzania: What we know and what we need to know for management under climate change
T2  - OCEAN & COASTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - WESTERN INDIAN-OCEAN
KW  - COASTAL WATERS
