TI  - Assessment of soil loss and amount of sediment exported and deposited in Upper Grande River Basin (Brazil) considering different scenarios
T2  - JOURNAL OF SOUTH AMERICAN EARTH SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Degraded areas
KW  - InVEST
KW  - SDR
