TI  - Can asset accumulation weigh the welfare status of mung bean farmers in lowland areas of South Ethiopia?
T2  - JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURE AND FOOD RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Asset accumulation
KW  - Mung bean
KW  - Multiple correspondence analysis
