TI  - Climate change and the emergence of Rift Valley fever virus: a pathological and environmental study of sheep jaundice in Egyptian slaughterhouses
T2  - BMC VETERINARY RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Rift valley fever
KW  - Jaundice
KW  - Pathology
KW  - Egypt
