TI  - An assessment of sustainable maize production under different management and climate scenarios for smallholder agro-ecosystems in KwaZulu-Natal, South Africa
T2  - PHYSICS AND CHEMISTRY OF THE EARTH
LA  - English
CP  - 6th WaterNet/Warfsa/GWP-SA Symposium
KW  - sustainability
