TI  - An oasis in the dryland of Kenya! The case of irrigation as an adaptation strategy among the transitioning pastoralists and agro-pastoralists of Laikipia County, Kenya
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLEANER PRODUCTION
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptation strategy
