TI  - Understanding vulnerability and resilience of Vietnamese pangasius farming in the context of the Covid-19 pandemic
T2  - AQUACULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - Pangasius farming
KW  - Vulnerability
KW  - Resilience
KW  - Covid-19
