TI  - Does adoption of climate-smart agriculture (CSA) practices improve farmers' crop income? Assessing the determinants and its impacts in Punjab province, Pakistan
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate-smart agriculture practices
KW  - Determinants
KW  - Conditional impact
KW  - Productivity and income
KW  - Punjab
KW  - ADAPTATION
KW  - YIELD
