TI  - Old wine, new bottles? Investigating the differential adoption of 'climate-smart' agricultural practices in western Kenya
T2  - JOURNAL OF RURAL STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - Climate smart agriculture
KW  - Conservation agriculture
KW  - Adoption
KW  - Climate change
