TI  - Ecosystem services valuation to build a matching funds scheme to finance adaptation to climate change in Puerto Vallarta, Mexico
T2  - MITIGATION AND ADAPTATION STRATEGIES FOR GLOBAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Ecosystem services
KW  - Contingent valuation
