TI  - Indigenous Tswana pig production characteristics and management practices in southern districts of Botswana
T2  - TROPICAL ANIMAL HEALTH AND PRODUCTION
LA  - English
KW  - Indigenous
KW  - Population
KW  - Production characteristics
KW  - Management practices
