TI  - The role of farmers' networks in sourcing planting material and information in a context of agroforestry transition in Madagascar
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Social network
KW  - Planting material
KW  - Information
KW  - Agrobiodiversity
