TI  - A Forecasting and Prediction Methodology for Improving the Blue Economy Resilience to Climate Change in the Romanian Lower Danube Euroregion
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - blue economy
KW  - fish stocks
KW  - water quality
KW  - machine learning
