TI  - Weather patterns, food security and humanitarian response in sub-Saharan Africa
T2  - PHILOSOPHICAL TRANSACTIONS OF THE ROYAL SOCIETY B-BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - emergency appeal
KW  - extreme weather
