TI  - From vulnerability to viability: integrating global evidence and Fijian insights for sugarcane resilience in SIDS
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - agricultural policy
KW  - climate adaptation
KW  - smallholder farmers
KW  - socio-ecological systems
