TI  - Institutional and technological innovations for sustained change in smallholder irrigation schemes in southern and Eastern Africa
T2  - AGRICULTURAL WATER MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Smallholder irrigation
KW  - Southern Africa
KW  - Transitions
KW  - Participatory approaches
KW  - Complementary interventions
