TI  - Heat stress causes economic and welfare disparities across agroecological zones in Burkina Faso
T2  - COMMUNICATIONS EARTH & ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - EXPOSURE
