TI  - Strategies for coping and adapting to flooding and their determinants: A comparative study of cases from Namibia and Zambia
T2  - PHYSICS AND CHEMISTRY OF THE EARTH
LA  - English
CP  - 17th WaterNet/WARFSA/GWPSA Symposium on Integrated Water Resources Management - Water Security, Sustainability and Development in Eastern and Africa Southern
