TI  - Local perceptions of change in climate and agroecosystems in the Indian Himalayas: A case study of the Kedarnath Wildlife Sanctuary (KWS) landscape, India
T2  - APPLIED GEOGRAPHY
LA  - English
KW  - CHANGE ADAPTATION
