TI  - Using soil-moisture drought indices to evaluate key indicators of agricultural drought in semi-arid Mediterranean Southern Africa
T2  - SCIENCE OF THE TOTAL ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Drought
KW  - Hydrological change
