TI  - RETRACTED: Factors impacting sugarcane production by small-scale farmers in KwaZulu-Natal Province-South Africa (Retracted Article)
T2  - HELIYON
LA  - English
KW  - Cobb-Douglas production
KW  - Small-scale farmers
KW  - Sugarcane production
